&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">├── archetypes: default.md是生成博文的模版
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">├── assets &lt;span class="c1"># 存放被 Hugo Pipes 处理的文件&lt;/span>
